[FILE:278:descriptions/desc.primary]
Leafpad is a GTK+ text editor that emphasizes simplicity. As development 
focuses on keeping weight down to a minimum, only the most essential 
features are implemented in the editor. Leafpad is simple to use, is 
easily compiled, requires few libraries, and starts up quickly.


